subject: Basketball (College)
Basketball
lead_paragraph: Breanna Stewart, Moriah Jefferson, Kia Nurse and Gabby Williams each had 13 points, and the No. 1 Connecticut women’s team easily overcame a slow start for its 50th straight victory, 76-37, over host Houston.
